## ğŸ›  Persyaratan Sistem

- PHP >= 8.2
- Composer
- Node.js & NPM
- MySQL / PostgreSQL / SQLite
- Laravel 10.x

---

## ğŸ“¦ Instalasi

### 1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/namauser/project-librain.git
cd project-librain
```

### 2. Install Dependency

```bash
composer install
npm install
```

### 3. Buat `.env` file

```bash
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
```

### 4. Jalankan Migrasi

```bash
php artisan migrate
```

Jika pakai seeder:

```bash
php artisan db:seed --class=AnggotaSeeder
```

### 5. Jalankan Server

```bash
php artisan serve
```

### 6. Jalankan Tailwind Watcher (jika menggunakan PostCSS)

```bash
npm run dev
```

